  <thing id="cMPSGGYBPm" name="Your Biggest Problem" description="If the tough attacks a foe with a melee attack, and foe does not take steps to defend itself or retaliate on its next turn (see full description), the tough gains a bonus to attack and damage rolls against the target on his next turn. \n\nThe tough demands that those they attacks pay attention to them, and can punish them if they don&apos;t.\n\nThis bonus increases by +1 for every 8 levels.\n\nA foe avoids triggering these bonuses if, before the tough&apos;s next turn, it takes a full defense action, a withdraw action, attacks the tough, makes the tough the target of a spell or effect, or includes the tough in the area of a spell or effect." compset="CustomSpec" summary="The tough demands that those they attack pay attention to them" uniqueness="unique">
