  <thing id="cMPSGGTDR" name="Damage Reduction" description="The tough gains DR 1/- . This stacks with damage reduction the tough gains from any one other source. This talent may be selected more than once, but no more often than once plus one per 4 full tough levels. \n\nEach time it is selected, the DR it provides increases by one." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Subtract damage taken dealt from a weapon or a natural attack">
